{"id":"341340423_A_Systematic_Review_of_Hidden_Markov_Models_and_Their_Applications","abstract":"The hidden Markov models are statistical models used in many real-world applications and communities. The use of hidden Markov models has become predominant in the last decades, as evidenced by a large number of published papers. In this survey, 146 papers (101 from Journals and 45 from Conferences/Workshops) from 93 Journals and 44 Conferences/Workshops are considered. The authors evaluate the literature based on hidden Markov model variants that have been applied to various application fields. The paper represents a short but comprehensive description of research on hidden Markov model and its variants for various applications. The paper shows the significant trends in the research on hidden Markov model variants and their applications.","authors":["Bhavya Mor","Sunita Garhwal","Ajay Loura"],"meta":["May 2020Archives of Computational Methods in Engineering 28(2)","DOI:10.1007/s11831-020-09422-4"],"references":["340800793_A_driving_intention_prediction_method_based_on_hidden_Markov_model_for_autonomous_driving","330881864_A_Hidden_Markov_Model_for_Indoor_Trajectory_Tracking_of_Elderly_People","325330467_Semi-automated_diagnosis_of_bearing_faults_based_on_a_hidden_Markov_model_of_the_vibration_signals","324723043_Log-Viterbi_algorithm_applied_on_second-order_hidden_Markov_model_for_human_activity_recognition","324240186_Diagnosis_and_Prognosis_of_Degradation_Process_via_Hidden_Semi-Markov_Model","323264386_Vector_Autoregressive_Hierarchical_Hidden_Markov_Models_for_Extracting_Finger_Movements_Using_Multichannel_Surface_EMG_Signals","322932560_A_Prediction_Mechanism_of_Energy_Consumption_in_Residential_Buildings_Using_Hidden_Markov_Model","322355200_Modeling_sepsis_progression_using_hidden_Markov_models","321036979_Machine_Learning_Based_Big_Data_Processing_Framework_for_Cancer_Diagnosis_Using_Hidden_Markov_Model_and_GM_Clustering","320389252_Smart_Annotation_of_Cyclic_Da